root: ^This is absolute horseshit! It’s mental that I’m even actually here this late at night!
^It’s even more warped that everyone from the class actually came. Then it’s even more stupid that even the Janitor showed up!
^I agree, why am I even here?
^Calm down, you’re already here, blowing up won’t do anything.
^I’m actually glad we get even more chances to study!
^How do you have so much energy?

c-1: ^Bite me, and don’t tell me to calm down.
c-3: ^Coffee? How else am I supposed to study this late at night... I don’t even normally study!
g-0: ^Seriously, I could understand the other students, but there’s no way the Janitor came in just to close the doors after we go up the stairs.
